TEXT.S: Tausa Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Cwosisyang ka alang Tausa. 12 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 592 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 98% niqan 578 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 2% niqan 14 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 73%, Tayal 10%, Amis 2%, Bunun 2%, Paiwan 1%, Truku 6%, ni rahuq na o 5%.
